'''module''' (plural: [[modules]])
# a [[self-contained]] [[component]] of a [[system]], often [[interchangeable]], which has a [[well-defined]] [[interface]] to the other components
#{{architecture}} a [[standard]] [[unit of measure]] used for determining the [[proportion]]s of a [[building]]
#{{computing}} a [[section]] of a [[program]]; a [[subroutine]]
#{{mathematics}} a set of quantities closed under addition and subtraction.
# a [[unit]] of [[education]] covering a single [[topic]]

